data.description: This STAND ALONE home has it all: BRAND NEW kitchen appliances, open-concept main floor with ample natural light throughout the living/dining/kitchen, plenty of storage, a half bathroom & direct access to the one-car garage with lots of storage and an EV charger. Head upstairs to the laundry room, a full bath & 4 spacious bedrooms, including the primary suite with soaring vaulted ceilings, walk-in closet & private 4-piece bath. Well-kept low-maintenance yard includes turf, a heated covered patio & a separate patio off the dining room, perfect for indoor/outdoor gatherings! Freshly painted interior & new carpeting upstairs! Ideal commuter location, near 509 & 99. Walkable to coffee shops, the library, restaurants, stores, parks & more!
